<item>
 <title>Безаман алу</title>
 <link>http://vse.la/marha-makaeva/bezaman-alu</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Дашо нур даржа деш,&lt;br /&gt;
